# CW Hub — Project Context

## What This Is
CW Hub is the **single centralized platform** for all Chatting Wizard operations. All employees (chatters, team leaders, COO) access it with their own account. It replaces Google Sheets for schedules, centralizes model metrics, and is progressively absorbing all external tools (School, Coaching Dashboard, Scripts) as native React pages.

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** React 19 + TypeScript + Vite
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS 4, dark theme, CW blue `#1d9bf0`
- **State:** Zustand
- **Backend:** Supabase (shared with CW-ChattingSchool)
  - URL: `https://bnmrdlqqzxenyqjknqhy.supabase.co`
  - Auth: email + password with invite codes
  - RLS on all tables
- **Hosting:** `hub.chattingwizard.com` (migrating to Cloudflare Pages)

